Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: secubox-admin
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, secubox-core (>= 1.0), python3-psutil
Description: SecuBox System Administration Dashboard
 Advanced system administration module for SecuBox.
 Provides web UI and API for system management tasks.
 .
 Features:
  - System status overview (CPU, memory, disk, load)
  - Systemd service management (start, stop, restart)
  - System logs viewer (journalctl integration)
  - Disk usage monitoring
  - Process manager (top processes by CPU/memory)
  - APT updates management
  - System reboot/shutdown with confirmation
 .
 Port Debian bookworm for SecuBox (CyberMind.fr).
